word_group.brief_definition: 怀孕的女孩；怀孕的女生

bilingual.source: It is important for pregnant women to get regular check-ups.
bilingual.target: 对怀孕的妇女来说，定期检查很重要。
她受到怀孕的大脑的影响
让我们从一只怀孕的章鱼开始说起。

bilingual.source: Robert had left 10 children and a pregnant widow.
bilingual.target: 罗伯特身后留下了10个孩子和一位怀孕的寡妇。

bilingual.source: The rumor that Patty is pregnant is spreading around.
bilingual.target: 佩蒂怀孕的谣言满天飞。

bilingual.source: German measles is a dangerous disease for pregnant women.
bilingual.target: 风疹对怀孕的妇女来说是一种危险的疾病。

bilingual.source: In addition, Pregnant Woman should not use this fragrance.
bilingual.target: 此外，怀孕的女性也不宜使用。

bilingual.source: Five porpoises asphyxiated, including three pregnant females.
bilingual.target: 这使得五头江豚几近窒息，其中包括三头怀孕的雌性江豚。

bilingual.source: Pregnant polar bears hibernate through the long dark winter.
bilingual.target: 怀孕的母北极熊会在漫长而黑暗的冬季进行冬眠。

list.abstract: pregnant（英[ˈpreɡnənt]，美[ˈpreɡnənt]），英语单词，形容词，意思为怀孕的；妊娠的；含义深远的。短语搭配有pregnant women（孕妇），例句为“It is best for pregnant women.（这对孕妇来说是最好的。）” pregnant形容词类近义词有cyetic、childing，相关反义词有nonpregnant，名词形式为pregnancy。
pregnant是R. Kelly演唱的歌曲，收录在专辑《Untitled》中。

yingyinNormal.en: Pregnant workers deserve to be treated fairly.
yingyinNormal.zh: 怀孕的员工应该得到公平地对待。

yingyinNormal.en: Rachel's really the one who's pregnant. What? Why bother?
yingyinNormal.zh: 怀孕的人是瑞秋？什么？干嘛那么麻烦呢？

yingyinNormal.en: I never thought I was pregnant. The test was for Blair.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我从没想过自己怀孕的事，我是为布莱尔买的验孕棒。

yingyinNormal.en: Her name is Erica. Hey, that pregnant girl's name was Erica.
yingyinNormal.zh: 女孩名叫艾瑞卡。那个怀孕的女孩不也叫艾瑞卡吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Well, I got TiVo. What's TiVo? It's slang for pregnant. Phoebe.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我有TIVo啊（互动式数字录放影机）。什么是TIVo ？就是怀孕的意思。菲比。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, my God, it was me, it was me. I'm the one who blabbed she was pregnant!
yingyinNormal.zh: 要死了，是我！是我传的！是我大嘴巴告诉别人她怀孕的！

yingyinNormal.en: The one at Caltech has a crazy wait list. I warned you, a lot of people apply when they're still pregnant.
yingyinNormal.zh: 加州理工那间候补名单超级长，我提醒过你，很多人怀孕的时候就开始申请了。

yingyinNormal.en: So, well, okay. So, maybe there's something I can do, you know, just to like help make sure I get pregnant?
yingyinNormal.zh: 也许我能做些什么事，来提高怀孕的机率？

yingyinNormal.en: Look, I was with Carol for four years before we got married and I wound up divorced from a pregnant lesbian.
yingyinNormal.zh: 听着，我跟卡萝结婚前在一起4年，最后跟一个怀孕的女同志离婚。

yingyinNormal.en: That's wrong and we have to choose policies that ensure pregnant workers are treated with dignity and respect.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是错误的，我们必须选择这样的政策，确保能够给予怀孕的员工尊严与尊重。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, if I'm pregnant. I want my baby to have a father and I won't change my mind about that, however much you offer.
yingyinNormal.zh: 要是我怀孕的话，我希望我的孩子有父亲，这一点我决心已定，无论你给多少。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, you know, my mom smoked pot when she was pregnant with me, and I turned out just fine. Hey, look, I have peach schnapps. Thank God.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我妈妈怀孕的时候也抽烟，但我身心发育完好。瞧，还有蜜桃酒呢！谢天谢地！

yingyinNormal.en: And then, just when she thinks I'm the best boyfriend in the world, then I'm going to tell her that my pregnant ex-girlfriend is living with me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当她觉得我是有史以来最棒的男朋友时，我会告诉她我怀孕的前女友跟我一起住。

yingyinNormal.en: Being pregnant is hard on your tummy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 怀孕真难吃东西。

yingyinNormal.en: How come you never said she was pregnant?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你怎么从来没说过她怀孕了？

yingyinNormal.en: You're not gonna tell him you're pregnant?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你不打算告诉他你怀孕了？

yingyinNormal.en: I'm pregnant. Ross? Ross? Okay, whenever you're ready.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我怀孕了，罗斯。罗斯。好吧，我等你准备好再说。

yingyinNormal.en: You were pregnant?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你怀孕了？

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, I mean you'll be pregnant. I mean pregnant. I know.
yingyinNormal.zh: 对啊，你会怀孕，怀孕耶。我知道啊。

yingyinNormal.en: She's also pregnant. Very pregnant. I need to find out who the father is.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而且她怀孕了，好几个月了，我得知道谁是孩子的父亲。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: I was four months <highlight>pregnant</highlight> (怀孕的) with my first child when my baby’s heart stopped beating.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 当我怀着第一个孩子，在四个月的时候，我孩子的心脏停止了跳动。
这对孕妇来说是最好的。

examination_example.sentence: If you are <highlight>pregnant</highlight> (怀孕的), ask a doctor before use.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果你怀孕了，请在使用前咨询医生。
